      <h4><b>One Pot Spaghetti</b></h4>
      
      <div class="text-left">
<p class="title"><b>INGREDIENTS:</b></p>
   <p>
      <li>1/2 Package spaghetti</li>
      <li>3 Cups water</li>
      <li>5 Dried tomatoes</li>
      <li>1 Piece of fresh turmeric</li>
      <li>1/4 Bunch of fresh basil</li>
      <li>1/2 Cup ground red pepper</li>
      <li>200 gr Oyster mushrooms</li>
      <li>4 Tbsp olive oil</li>
      <li>2 Garlic cloves</li>
      <li>Black pepper</li>
      <li>Salt</li>
  </p>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3"></div>
  <div class="text-left col-sm-12 col-md-6">
      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Wipe the mushrooms and chop.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Chop the dried tomatoes,  fresh turmeric, fresh basil, dried red peppers and garlic then add to the pan with the spaghetti.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Combine all the ingredients in the pan and cook for about 8-10 minutes. Don't filter the water.</li>
    </div>
<div class="col-md-3"></div>
</div>
